node.text:
My Chef making sure food he cooks is clean and safe to put in mouth!
We used @59s_singapore to sterilise their toys, especially their pretend play food, which they tend to put inside their mouth. 
The toy steriliser can fill toys as much as a tray of ikea TROFAST
Storage box, 42x30x10 cm.
All it takes is 3mins to sterilise!
The adorable little chef and his sterilizer  is in action ❤️😆
@itsjeanlum yes certainly !! Too hot to resist haha
Really Love to see him flaunt his cute body ! He is real adorable !!
Oh wow...This item is a must buy!
Your chef too adorable. Can cook for didi Damon?
Aww... 💕 way too cutee leii!! Our family super love sterilizers 🙌🏻💕 that work so effectively n fast
Wow it doesn’t look that big but can pack so much? If I had one I’d sterilise non-stop I think 😆
